      interface  DiscreteUncertainObject
      Interface for discrete uncertain objects, that are represented by a finite (possibly weighted) number of samples.

      Modifier and Type Class Description
      class  AbstractUncertainObject
      Abstract base implementation for UncertainObjects, providing shared functionality such as bounding box access and random generation.

      Gaussian model for uncertain objects, sampled from a 3-sigma bounding box.

      Continuous uncertain object model using a uniform distribution on the bounding box.

      Unweighted implementation of discrete uncertain objects.
